    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_7854674638016567360.png",
                "id": "talent18518",
                "key": "重钳碎击",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "重钳碎击"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>；如果本角色附属有至少7层<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳</span>，则此伤害+1。</p><p>然后，本角色附属2层<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳。<br><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">护盾</span></p><p>每层提供1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>，保护所附属角色。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/0ae22e52af3cd0693c58a452cef1d284_6030061599692901636.png",
                "id": "talent58095",
                "key": "烈焰燃绽",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "烈焰燃绽"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>本角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能：炽烈轰破</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">炽烈轰破</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>（需准备1个行动轮）</p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，对敌方所有后台角色造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>。本角色每附属有2层<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳</span>，就使此技能造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>+1。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">护盾</span></p><p>每层提供1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>，保护所附属角色。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/a9c20ff9f809e176b5b49857c4ad1153_553924178864178727.png",
                "id": "talent31074",
                "key": "战阵爆轰",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "战阵爆轰"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">战斗开始时：</span>初始附属5层<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方执行任意行动后：</span>如果我方场上存在重甲蟹壳以外的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>状态或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>出战状态，则将其全部移除；每移除1个，就使角色附属2层<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重甲蟹壳</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">护盾</span></p><p>每层提供1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>，保护所附属角色。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/926ad2c8e8892093800da58cea01f2ad_5175909966015894519.png",
                "id": "talent40079",
                "key": "帝王甲胄",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "帝王甲胄"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着火元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/02/157749474/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3965784426612710490.png",
                "id": "talent95534",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span></strong></p><p>有些技能无法被直接使用，而是需要一定次数的行动轮来进行<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>。</p><p>轮到一位牌手行动时，如果该牌手的「出战角色」正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能，则跳过该牌手的行动；如果技能已经完成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>，角色将会在此时直接使用此技能。（此类需要<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>的技能，无法触发「使用技能后」「角色引发元素反应后」等效果。）</p><p>只有「出战角色」才能<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>技能的「出战角色」被切换到后台，技能的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备</span>就会被打断。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/1ef525b101a31611b9fe2cc1b0a59aa8_254722055947068757.png",
                "id": "talent80220",
